Package pl.polsl.lab1.krzysztof.gach.model

package pl.polsl.lab1.krzysztof.gach.model
Contains the model components of the application, representing the core data and business logic. Key classes in this package:
  • Board: Represents the game board and its layout.
  • Cell: Represents individual cells on the game board.
  • InvalidNameException: Custom exception for handling invalid player names.
  • Player: Represents a player in the game, including their attributes and score.
  • PlayersList: Manages a list of players participating in the game.
  • Class
    Description
    Board
    The Board class represents a game board consisting of a 2D array of cells.
    Cell
    The Cell class represents a single cell on the game board.
    InvalidNameException
    Custom exception class to handle invalid names.
    Player
    The Player class represents a player in the game.
    PlayersList
    The PlayersList class manages a list of players in the game.
